title: "Effective Altruism" is Rubbish, Innit? (Veganism / Ecology / Animal Rights)
description:
If you care about the future of the vegan movement, read the essay, here's the link:
https://medium.com/@harrisonnathan/the-actual-number-is-almost-surely-higher-92c908f36517
Nathan Harrison, "the actual number is almost certainly higher", an essay in large part about A.C.E. (Animal Charity Evaluators) and the effective altruism / effective activism paradigm.
